<div type="addressee">
<ab>Cristoff von <expan>Layming<ex>en</ex></expan>,
                            <expan>hawbtm<ex>an</ex></expan> zu Lawff</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan>
<expan>hawbtm<ex>an</ex></expan>, uns <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        fürbracht <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan> guten frewnde der von Lübeck und
                        der <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan> stette daselbsumb
                            <expan>erb<ex>er</ex>n</expan> botten, die
                            <expan>yecz<ex>unden</ex></expan> bey uns seyn, wie sie auf
                                <expan>gest<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>ein<ex>en</ex></expan> iren <expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan> bey uns
                        gefertigt <expan>hett<ex>en</ex></expan>, heym zu reiten, dem ein pferd und
                        etlich <expan>and<ex>er</ex></expan> sein hab von
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>geselle<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan> und zu ewch gen Lawff
                            <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> sey. <expan>Daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> wir
                                <expan>Eb<ex>erhart</ex></expan> Hasen,
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan>, zu ewch <expan>schik<ex>en</ex></expan>, dem
                        wir <expan>befolhe<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan>, mit ew <expan>davo<ex>n</ex></expan> zu
                        reden. Et <expan>roga<ex>mus</ex></expan> in <expan>for<ex>ma</ex></expan>
                        credencie. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut
                        <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
